'''''Modern Philology'' volume 96, number 4''' is an issue of the journal ''[[Wikipedia:Modern Philology|Modern Philology]]''.

The article "Lewis and Cambridge" by Brian Barbour includes a portion of [[Letter to Henry Willink|a letter to Sir Henry Willink]] from [[J.R.R. Tolkien]].<ref name=Addenda>{{webcite|author=[[Christina Scull]], [[Wayne G. Hammond]]|articleurl=http://www.hammondandscull.com/addenda/chronology.html|articlename=Addenda and Corrigenda to ''The J.R.R. Tolkien Companion and Guide'' (2006) Vol. 1: Chronology|dated=|website=HS|accessed=20 May 2012}}</ref>
